item.title: Bouquet of the Day!
item.dc:creator: o8lyil
item.content:encoded:
Baffled about what to send? Or perhaps you want to surprise them with a one-of-a-kind, artisanal arrangement? With our Bouquet of the Day bouquets, you have many price options to choose from and our expert florists exercise their creativity to design a beautiful bouquet using the freshest seasonal flowers available.
When you send a Bouquet of the Day bouquet, you can feel confident knowing one of our expert designers will create an unforgettable flower arrangement with their own signature style and flair. Please note that flowers and designs will vary as our artisan florists work with the freshest, in-season flowers and their own personal inspiration - but you can be sure your bouquet will delight!
item.excerpt:encoded: Bouquet of the Day bouquet
